Description

Supplementary data and COPASI modelling file for the analysis of Rubisco compartments. To access the manuscript follow this link: https://doi.org/10.1101/2020.07.08.125609

Steps to reproduce

The COPASI model files can be reproduced using the ordinary differential equations in the Supplementary Information and using the data tables provided in the main text. COPASI is freely available software from copasi.org. A preprint of this manuscript is available at https://doi.org/10.1101/2020.07.08.125609
